### Cinema API — коллекция запросов
### Базовый URL: http://localhost:8080
### Переменные (Postman/IDE): baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ========== CRUD: Customers ==========
### Список клиентов
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers

### Создать клиента
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Новый Клиент",
  "email": "new@example.com"
}

### Получить клиента по id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1

### Обновить клиента
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Иван Петров (обновлён)",
  "email": "ivan@mail.ru"
}

### Удалить клиента
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/4

### ========== CRUD: Movies ==========
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Интерстеллар",
  "genre": "Фантастика",
  "durationMinutes": 169
}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/1

PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Матрица",
  "genre": "Фантастика",
  "durationMinutes": 136
}

# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/4

### ========== CRUD: Halls ==========
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/halls

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/halls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Зал 4",
  "capacity": 80
}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/halls/1

PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/halls/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Зал 1",
  "capacity": 120
}

# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/halls/4

### ========== CRUD: Screenings ==========
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/screenings

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/screenings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie": { "id": 1 },
  "hall": { "id": 1 },
  "startTime": "2025-03-20T19:00:00"
}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/screenings/1

PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/screenings/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movie": { "id": 1 },
  "hall": { "id": 1 },
  "startTime": "2025-03-15T18:30:00"
}

# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/screenings/4

### ========== CRUD: Tickets ==========
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "screening": { "id": 1 },
  "customer": { "id": 1 },
  "price": 400.0
}

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1

PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 450.0
}

# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/4

### ========== БИЗНЕС-ОПЕРАЦИИ ==========

### 1. Покупка билета (buy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/buy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "screeningId": 1,
  "price": 350.0
}

### 2. Возврат билета (refund)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/refund/3

### 3. Сеансы по фильму
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/screenings?movieId=1

### 4. Свободные места на сеанс
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/available-seats?screeningId=1

### 5. Покупка нескольких билетов (bulk)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": 2,
  "screeningId": 1,
  "quantity": 3,
  "pricePerTicket": 350.0
}

### Доп: Билеты клиента
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/customer/1/tickets

### ========== Сценарий: создать данные → операция → результат ==========
### Шаг 1: Проверяем свободные места
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/available-seats?screeningId=1

### Шаг 2: Покупаем билет
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/buy
# Content-Type: application/json
# {"customerId": 3, "screeningId": 1, "price": 350.0}

### Шаг 3: Снова смотрим свободные места (должно уменьшиться)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/available-seats?screeningId=1

### Шаг 4: Билеты клиента
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/booking/customer/3/tickets
